What are the benefits of using an abstract method?

Ans -
    1. In java abstraction is basically using for hiding the unnecessary
    data from the user and try to focus on functionality.
    2. It increase the efficiency of the program.
    3. It reduces  the complexity of the program.
    4. In abstract method it also using the same way. When ever
    we just need the method new just declared in a super class.
    5.In abstract method it have flexibilty also.